data.description: Welcome to this charming traditional brick ranch home located in Ardmore! Updated Kitchen with SS appliances. Unique built-in bar height peninsula smartly positioned between the kitchen and living room. Fireplace, built-in shelves, recessed lighting and large picture window in the living room. Main level has 3 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms. Basement has finished space currently being used as a 4th bedroom (not included in square footage due to ceiling height) and another full bath! Basement den has a fireplace and reading nook with bench storage! Unfinished basement space for workshop, storage and laundry. There's more...Fenced back yard with storage shed, spacious deck, paved patio and brick fire pit! Convenient to hospitals, shopping and downtown!
